code: @Nonnull @Override Collection<? extends MetricStore.ComponentMetricStore> getStores(MetricStore store, HandlerRequest<EmptyRequestBody, AggregateTaskManagerMetricsParameters> request) {     List<ResourceID> taskmanagers = request.getQueryParameter(TaskManagersFilterQueryParameter.class).     if (taskmanagers.isEmpty()) {         return store.getTaskManagers().values().     } else {         Collection<MetricStore.TaskManagerMetricStore> taskmanagerStores = new ArrayList<>(taskmanagers.size()).         for (ResourceID taskmanager : taskmanagers) {             MetricStore.TaskManagerMetricStore taskManagerMetricStore = store.getTaskManagerMetricStore(taskmanager.getResourceIdString()).             if (taskManagerMetricStore != null) {                 taskmanagerStores.add(taskManagerMetricStore).             }         }         return taskmanagerStores.     } }
